[21:38] <jnthn> Including coping with native callbacks coming on different threads etc.
[21:39] <jnthn> I believe DBIish does have some things one must be aware of in a threaded application
[21:39] <jnthn> In a $dayjob project we're using DB::Pg instead which seems to do pretty well on the thread stuff (as in, it seems this was thought about)
